<div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679513464437" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1679513464437"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">What is Shop Repurpose</h1></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679513622647" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1679513622647"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Old Standard TT&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;">Shop Repurpose is a nonprofit organization that utilizes the resale of luxury items to raise funds and develop programs to support the health and wellbeing of women and families, empower individuals through mentorship and workforce opportunities, and provide conscious-minded communities to contribute to a more sustainable world.</span><br></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679513696417" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1679513696417"><div class="elm gf-elm-center" data-align="left"><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679513657678" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1679513657678"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">How does the donation process at Shop Repurpose works?</h1></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679513703634" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1679513703634"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>We accept merchandise donations as long as they meet Repurpose standards and comply with the following:&nbsp;</p><p>The conditions of Items we receive are either Brand New, Unused, Unworn or Pre-Owned (lightly used -look like new). A trained stylist will approve items donated before reaching our facility (on site or online TBD).&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Brands: We currently carry the following designers listed here. This list serves as an example of designers we carry, but not limited to only these brands.   We do not focus on designers that have a strong presence in outlet stores or discount retailers.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>We guarantee that items we sell are 100%authentic. Please note that brands sold are not partnered or affiliated with Repurpose Wardrobe.</p><p>Items must be clean/washed before scheduling donation</p><p><br></p><p>When to donate: Schedule and confirm donations through emailing e-info@shoprepurpose.org.  We have a weekly max capacity for receiving goods.</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" class="element-wrap" data-description="" data-key="text-block" id="e-1679513435403" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1679513435403"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><h3><b>What is the donation process?&nbsp;</b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">We accept merchandise donations as long as they meet Repurpose standards and comply with the following:&nbsp;</span></h3><ul style="text-align: left;"><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">The conditions of Items we receive are either Brand New, Unused, Unworn or Pre-Owned (lightly used -look like new). A trained stylist will approve items donated before reaching our facility (on site or online TBD).&nbsp;</span></h3></li><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Brands: We currently carry the following designers listed </span><a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/pages/designer-list"><span style="font-weight: 400;">here</span></a><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;"> This list serves as an example of designers we carry, but not limited to only these brands. &nbsp; We do not focus on designers that have a strong presence in outlet stores or discount retailers.&nbsp;</span></h3></li></ul><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">We guarantee that items we sell are 100%authentic. Please note that brands sold are not partnered or affiliated with Repurpose Wardrobe.</span></h3><ul style="text-align: left;"><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Items must be clean/washed before scheduling donation</span></h3></li><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">When to donate: Schedule and confirm donations through emailing e-info@shoprepurpose.org.&nbsp; We have a weekly max capacity for receiving goods.</span></h3></li></ul><table style="float: left;"><tbody><tr><td><h3><b>Does Repurpose donate what you can’t sell and is everything that is sent to Repurpose on the tax itemized sheet? </b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">That is correct. We will send over an itemized list of the items that we have received.&nbsp; If a customer asks for an estimated pricing on FMV (resale)&nbsp; we will happily provide (otherwise we leave this blank).&nbsp; Items that are donated that we DO NOT intake into Repurpose inventory are donated to either Strive or Dress for Success.&nbsp;</span></h3><h3><b>What happens with the items received that you don’t believe you can sell?</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Any </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">items we can’t sell in our store&nbsp; are donated to the following organizations:</span></h3><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strive&nbsp;</span></h3></li><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dress for Success&nbsp;</span></h3></li></ul><h3><b>Understanding that you are looking for a designer level of items, do you accept items that are of equivalent value/type but not included on the list (e.g. Marc Jacobs)?</b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">To read more about the designer we accept visit our <a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/pages/designer-list" target="_blank" title="ShopRepurpose list of accepted designers" rel="noopener noreferrer">designer list</a>.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;Our list is just an idea of designers we carry. We will accept other items of similar value. Examples of brands which we will not accept in our store, and not limited to are;&nbsp; J. Crew or Zara.&nbsp;</span></h3><h3><b>How are items valued? Does the person donating value them? Or are values included on itemized tax receipt? </b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">If requested, we can share our pricing on items for tax purposes. If items are of high resale value (above 10K) and they want to take a tax write-off, we offer several names of appraisers that will work independent of our organization.&nbsp; The donor has to incur the cost of the appraisal, but there appraisers are offering reduced rates for us as a nonprofit organization. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;</span></h3><h3><b>What is your return policy if I use a discount code?</b></h3><h3><b>&nbsp;</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">It is the final sale.&nbsp;</span></h3><h3><b>What is your shipping policy?&nbsp;</b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Due to the ongoing developments with COVID-19 the protection of our customers is a top priority and all the necessary precautions are being put in place to ensure the wellbeing of our customers. All economy orders will ship within 1-3 business days. We are unable to offer refunds for packages lost or stolen after delivery to a customer's given address. You will receive an order confirmation email after placing your order to the email address provided. Once your order has shipped, you will receive a shipping confirmation email that will include your tracking number and an estimated delivery date.&nbsp; International. We do ship internationally; prices vary depending on region/country. The customer is responsible for paying any fees in customs. &nbsp; For additional information or questions please email us at&nbsp; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">e-info@shoprepurose.org</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp; to reach a customer representative.</span></h3><h3><b>Is it safe to shop from your site?</b></h3><h3><b>&nbsp;</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">The health and safety of our customers&nbsp; has always been our first priority. We have enhanced safety measures&nbsp; to maximize protection.</span></h3><h3><b>Do I need an account to place an order?</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Yes, you&nbsp; need an account to shop with us. The benefits of having an account with us are the following:&nbsp;</span></h3><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Track your orders and review past purchases</span></h3></li><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Save your address and card details so you can shop even quicker in future</span></h3></li><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Seamless check out&nbsp;</span></h3></li></ul><h3><b>Can I amend or cancel an item from my order?</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Depending on the status of your order, it may be possible to cancel an item.. Please note, we’re unable to combine or add an item to an existing order.</span></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you need to make any amendments to your purchase, please email our customer service as soon as possible. e-info@shoprepurpose.org</span></h3><h3><b>What do I do if I think an item that I purchased from your site is faulty?&nbsp;</b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Simply email e-info@shoprepurpose.org and we’ll look into this for you.&nbsp; Please provide your order number and photographs of your item.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;</span></h3><h3><b>How do I contact your PR or Team? </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">You can send an email to the following addresses:</span></h3><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Press and media: social@shoprepurpose.org</span></h3></li><li style="font-weight: 400;"><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Potential contributors - &nbsp;operations@shoprepurpose.org</span></h3></li></ul><h3><b>Where can I find information on sustainability?</b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">To read more about how Repurpose&nbsp; is creating a more sustainable future, visit the <a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/blogs/news">blog</a>.&nbsp;</span></h3><h3><b>Where can I find information on nonprofits you partner with?</b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">To read more about the nonprofits Repurpose partners with, visit our <a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/pages/https-shoprepurpose-org-pages-about">About Us</a>&nbsp;page.</span></h3><h3><b>How can I send a monetary donation?</b></h3><h3><b>&nbsp;</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">To send a monetary donation to Repurpose,&nbsp;please click <a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/pages/donate-now">here</a></span></h3><h3><b>How can I donate clothes?&nbsp;</b></h3><h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">To donate to Repurpose <a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/pages/contact-us">Contact Us</a></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;to schedule a pick up time, discuss items being donated, and assess if you need any complimentary virtual assistance. Read more by visiting our <a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/pages/get-involved-shop-repurpose" title="get invoved">Get Involved</a> page<a href="https://shoprepurpose.org/pages/get-involved-shop-repurpose" title="GET INVOLVED">.</a>&nbsp;</span></h3></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><!--gfsplit--><script>window.__gemStoreData = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid.bestWayAddToCart = 1;</script>
